darks.orm.app
接口 SqlSession

所有超级接口：
java.io.Serializable, SqlBaseSession, SqlBeanSession, SqlJdbcSession
所有已知实现类：
SessionSupport, SqlSessionImpl
public interface SqlSession
extends java.io.Serializable, SqlJdbcSession, SqlBeanSession

SQL session interface, developers use the framework of the main entrance.Most of the API function on this interface.

SqlSession.java

For example; 

 SqlSession session = SqlSessionFactory.getSession();

JDK1.5

1.0.0 v05/03/2012
